>이력서와 포트폴리오를 이메일로 제출하세요.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We accept applications on an irregular basis. Submit your resume and portfolio by email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">PRESS</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>인터뷰와 출판 문의는 이메일로 요청 내용과 연락처를 남겨주시면 회신을 드립니다.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For interviews and publication inquiries, we will reply if you send us your request and contact information by email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">CONTACT</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TEL <a href=\"tel:029239789\">82+ 02 923 9789</a><br>FAX 82+ 02 923 9780<br>MAIL <a href=\"mailto:office@emaa.co.kr\">office@emaa.co.kr</a><br>INSTAGRAM <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ema_aaa_/\">@ema_aaa_</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/tabgroup -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/tabgroup {\"name\":\"acf/tabgroup\",\"data\":{\"tab_name\":\"DIRECT MESSAGE\",\"_tab_name\":\"field_6469bfab90a73\"},\"mode\":\"preview\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>설계 문의는 메일로 요청드립니다.<br>아래의 폼에서 바로 보내기도 가능하며, 연락처를 남겨주시면 전화를 드립니다</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/emailjsform {\"name\":\"acf/emailjsform\",\"data\":{\"service_id\":\"service_3wo8rwx\",\"_service_id\":\"field_646b2109fd8eb\",\"template_id\":\"template_tusw00s\",\"_template_id\":\"field_646b2709ed8b0\",\"public_key\":\"xspKx05eLf9C4-XJL\",\"_public_key\":\"field_646b271ded8b1\"},\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n<!-- /wp:acf/tabgroup -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/customcolums -->','CONTACT','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2023-05-22 08:28:31','2023-05-22 08:28:31','',0,'http://ema.local/?page_id=25',0,'page','',0);
