tr><tr><td>2015.10.</td><td>2015 공동체주택 설계공모전, 최우수상, 서울특별시</td></tr><tr><td>2014.04.</td><td>2014 김수근 건축상 프리뷰상, 김수근문화재단</td></tr><tr><td>2012.02.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/aboutcolums -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','ABOUT','','inherit','closed','closed','','16-revision-v1','','','2023-05-20 14:39:05','2023-05-20 14:39:05','',16,'http://ema.local/?p=185',0,'revision','',0);
